      "acceptanceCriteria": "Solver must demonstrate correct implementation of governing equations via benchmark problems relevant to rotating machinery flows.",
      "rationale": "Code verification performed using Taylor-Green vortex and lid-driven cavity benchmarks. Observed order of accuracy consistent with theoretical order for the discretization schemes employed."
