      "acceptanceCriteria": "Grid convergence index (GCI) must be reported for hemolysis index QoI with GCI < 5% on the fine grid.",
      "rationale": "Three-level mesh refinement study performed (3.2M, 8.7M, 22.1M cells). Richardson extrapolation yields GCI of 2.8% for the relative hemolysis index on the fine mesh. Achieves level 3, exceeding MRL 2 requirement."
