      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Predicted hemolysis index must agree with experimental measurements within combined simulation and experimental uncertainty bands.",
      "rationale": "Predicted normalized index of hemolysis (NIH) values agree with published FDA pump experimental data within 12% across all 5 operating points, well within the combined uncertainty envelope. Monte Carlo UQ confirms output variability is bounded."
    },
    {
