      "acceptanceCriteria": "Turbulence model selection and hemolysis power-law model must be justified relative to available experimental evidence for blood pump flows.",
      "rationale": "SST k-omega turbulence model selected based on literature evidence for rotating machinery with adverse pressure gradients. Giersiepen-Wurzinger hemolysis power-law model applied consistently with published FDA pump validation studies."
