    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. The 6 not-assessed factors are acceptable per MRL 2 scoping. Comprehensive Monte Carlo UQ confirms that output uncertainty in the relative hemolysis index is bounded with 95th-percentile RH = 0.87 < 1.0 acceptance criterion. The model is judged credible for the intended COU of identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device.",
